      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "thanks these are good. i think the warm grey is nice. can you try a couple more options that use some darker, deeper tones? maybe like a navy or a charcoal? just to see if we can add a bit more depth without losing the professional vibe.",
